{"word":"Jehoiakim","slug":"jehoiakim","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jehoiakim</b> <a href=\"#/H3079\">H3079</a> <br/> Called also Eliakim.<br/> King of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=15'>1Ch 3:15</a><br/> Ancestor of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=11'>Mat 1:11</a><br/> Wicked reign and final overthrow of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=37'>2Ki 23:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=6'>2Ki 24:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=8'>2Ch 36:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=19'>Jer 22:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=26&verse=23'>Jer 26:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36'>Jer 36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=2'>Dan 1:2</a><br/> Dies, and is succeeded by his son, Jehoiachin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=6'>2Ki 24:6</a>"}]}